Project overview:
2 players are in a match
a clock starts
players have a time period to guess as many words in wordle format
at the end of the time, each player's score is tallied up
player with higher score wins

round starts:
player gets 3 min to guess as many word as possible
if they run out of attempts, show the word and go to next word
tally up their total score at the end of round
whoever has the highest game score at the end wins
